text:
It just feels like a regular big park, but...
Is this really a "nice place"?

Yeah, that's right. During this season,
it shows us a very beautiful scenery.

I'm glad I could come here with Mamimi.
Meeting you in town earlier was truly lucky, wasn't it?

Is it really that lucky...?
Seems a bit exaggerated, doesn't it?

Not at all. Mamimi's schedule just happened to be
free, and she came all the way here with me.

I feel so lucky, like I should thank the heavens...
Yeah, maybe we should be grateful to the gods.
Thank you for accompanying me, Mamimi.

Well, it's not like...
I had a specific place in mind to go to or anything.

If that's the case, then I must escort you
properly so that you can enjoy it, Mamimi.
...You don't have to go that far.
